            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " are somewhat ignored when painting a damp picture of Britain, in favour of targeting British Leyland’s most lampooned output – the Austin Allegro, Morris Marina and ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
